The '''''Yavin''''' was a Star Cruiser commanded by [[General/Legends|General]] [[Wedge Antilles/Legends|Wedge Antilles]] during the [[Battle of Almania]].

==History==
This powerful warship was the flagship of a task force sent to deal with [[Dark Jedi/Legends|Dark Jedi]] [[Kueller]]. Fighting alongside the [[Tatooine (starship)|''Tatooine'']] and [[Calamari (starship)|''Calamari'']], Wedge managed to defeat the trio of [[Victory II-class Star Destroyer/Legends|''Victory II''-class Star Destroyers]] and secure a victory for the [[New Republic/Legends|New Republic]].

